snippet.title: Espen Kraft
snippet.description:
Maker of  80s inspired synthpop, synth music and retro emotions.

This channel is all about showing 80s studio gear in action and to show how synth music can be made today, old school. Tutorials, demos and workflow.

Please join me on social media:

https://www.facebook.com/espenkraftmusic
https://soundcloud.com/espenkraft
https://twitter.com/EspenKraft
https://www.instagram.com/espenkraft/

https://www.espenkraft.com
